{"tid":1386172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有市民向警方申請周六於旺角遊行","createTime":"2019-07-30T09:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:06:14.000Z","uid":20933,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5c101115b0539de75b7386b61ad32fe1bab91ef6","tid":1386172,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】有市民計劃周六於旺角遊行，到旺角警署申請不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n申請人伍永德指，遊行的目的是堅持五大訴求，原本預計有一萬人參與，他說警方在會上建議將預計的遊行人數由一萬人減至五千人，並將遊行結束的時間由晚上九時提早至七時，伍永德向警方表示同意。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，已經應警方要求更改遊行路線的起點，在晏架街足球場出發，途經彌敦道至麥花臣籃球場，他引述警方表示，將於48小時內通知會否批出不反對通知書。"},{"pid":"290eff3ea45d66d6001ff5262eaa310764194bec","tid":1386172,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:22:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=357327\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357327&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=b5320a58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357327&h=70022e77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=357327</a>"},{"pid":"57d771ccfdac6a9a2eec8bed3bc33bbf926da0e8","tid":1386172,"uid":280522,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"話知你想幾點完, 出黎行宜家都有共識, 就係要保護自己"},{"pid":"492271aeda61488927fa03615d9bd79b04df9227","tid":1386172,"uid":270912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8fb68c3c4bad2451411f4261398125bec9cf5fb","tid":1386172,"uid":285899,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:25:11.000Z","msg":"唔好無目的死守 be water不是撤 是轉場去下個目標<br />\n唔好又送頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea00e2bc9748dfd3cf95cf57844f4e47978e3569","tid":1386172,"uid":235580,"like":0,"disli